NK005(ca)005:0: dpal sangs rgyas mnyam sbyor gyi dkyil 'khor la brten
NK005(ca)005:1: pa'i mchog gi sbyin sreg ye shes snang ba bzhugs
NK005(ca)005:3: bla ma dang dpal 'khor los sgyur ba drug gi
NK005(ca)005:4: dkyil 'khor la gus pa chen pos phyag 'tshal zhing
NK005(ca)005:5: skyabs su mchi'o // de yang gsang snying la /
NK005(ca)005:6: dbyibs dang kha dog mtshan ldan par //
NK005(ca)005:7: zhal du gyur pa'i me bos la //
NK005(ca)005:8: bza' btung bro ba'i tshogs rnams kyi //
NK005(ca)005:9: las bzhi'i mchod pa rab tu sbyin //
NK005(ca)005:10: zhes pa ltar rgyud lung gi dkyil 'khor so so
NK005(ca)005:11: la brten pa'i las bzhi'i sbyin sreg gi rim pa
NK005(ca)005:12: ni gzhan du gsal ba ltar shes par bya zhing
NK005(ca)005:13: / 'dir dpal sangs rgyas thams cad mnyam par sbyor
NK005(ca)005:14: ba'i dkyil 'khor la brten nas byang chub zhi ba
NK005(ca)005:15: dam pa'i go 'phang la dmigs pa'i phyir mchog gi
NK005(ca)005:16: sreg blugs la 'jug pa'i rim pa gsal bar bya
NK005(ca)005:21: gang du bya ba'i gnas dge zhing shis pa'i sa
NK005(ca)005:22: phyogs der gtso bo'i rnal 'byor la gnas bzhin pas
NK005(ca)005:23: gzhi bdag la cha gsum la sogs pa'i gtor ma
NK005(ca)005:24: btang / sa'i lha mo la dkar gtor dang nyer spyod bshams la /
NK005(ca)005:26: rgyal ba sh+aakya seng ge yis //
NK005(ca)005:27: bdud sde mngon par bcom pa'i tshe //
NK005(ca)005:28: dbang gyur sa yi lha mo khyod //
NK005(ca)005:29: gtor ma bzhes la sa 'di slong //
NK005(ca)005:31: nad med tshe dang dbang 'byor dang //
NK005(ca)005:34: rdo rje dang bcas pa'i thal mo sa la bkram ste yi dam gyi nga rgyal dang /
NK005(ca)005:35: rtsa sngags kyis sbyang ba lan gsum gyis sa bzung rjes /
NK005(ca)005:36: sa gzhi yang rang bzhin med par shes pa'i chos nyid la dran pa mngon du bzhag nas /
NK005(ca)005:37: sh+au nya t+aa'i sngags brjod pa ni bden pa gnyis kyis sbyang ba'o //
NK005(ca)005:38: gnyis pa dngos gzhi la'ang sbyor dngos gnyis las /
NK005(ca)005:40: bkra shis pa'i sa la stegs bu gru bzhir byas
NK005(ca)005:41: pa'i steng du thab khung zlum po rgyar khru gang
NK005(ca)005:42: / dpangs su phyed longs pa nas phyir 'phyang mu
NK005(ca)005:43: ran rgya dpangs sor bzhi pa re'i kha khyer nang
NK005(ca)005:44: du phags kyis gzhol ba la rdo rje'i phreng ba
NK005(ca)005:45: / dang / mu ran la me ris bskor /
NK005(ca)005:46: thab kyi dbus su rtse mo shar bstan gyi rdo rje dkar po sor brgyad pa dang /
NK005(ca)005:47: stegs bu'i steng zur bzhir zla phyed rdo rjes mtshan pa bya /
NK005(ca)005:48: brus thab byed na rgya dpangs dang rnam pa des mtshon nas rigs pas dpags la /
NK005(ca)005:50: stegs bu'i steng du dri bzang ba byung lnga bdud
NK005(ca)005:51: rtsi lnga rnams chang dang sbyar bas chag chag btab
NK005(ca)005:52: / de'i steng du tshangs zur gyi thig btab /
NK005(ca)005:53: dbus nas mtho gang zlum por bskor bas nad rgya
NK005(ca)005:54: khru gang 'ong ba'i phyi rol sor bzhi re bskyor
NK005(ca)005:55: bas mchu dang kha khyer gnyis 'byung ba'i nang me
NK005(ca)005:56: ri dang / phyi mar rdo rje'i phreng ba zur bzhir zla phyed rdo rje /
NK005(ca)005:57: lte bar rdo rje dkar po rtse lnga pa bri /
NK005(ca)005:58: 'o ma can gyi shing gi rtse mo'i cha'am dgon
NK005(ca)005:59: pa'i ba lang gi lci ba srog chags med pas
NK005(ca)005:60: thab kyi dpangs tshad las cung zad dman pa zlum
NK005(ca)005:61: por brtsigs pa'i shar lhor me tshang bca' /
NK005(ca)005:62: thab kyi grwa bzhir mnga' bzhi btsugs pa srad bu
NK005(ca)005:63: dkar pos bsnol mar sgrel ba la dar dkar pos
NK005(ca)005:64: dgag / de'i shar lho'i zur du mda' dar dmar po gzugs /
NK005(ca)005:65: thab kyi mdun du rang nyid 'dug pa'i stan dkar zhing 'jam pa dang /
NK005(ca)005:66: de'i g.yas g.yon du stegs bu khebs dkar po dang
NK005(ca)005:67: ldan pa re'i g.yas kyi steng logs su ba las
NK005(ca)005:69: 'o ma can nam ba lu lcang ma la sogs
NK005(ca)005:70: pa'i rung mthun gyi shing gi rtse mo'i cha las
NK005(ca)005:71: byung ba'i yam shing mtho gang ba'i rtse mo mar
NK005(ca)005:76: mar khu sogs bsres pa' zho zan /
NK005(ca)005:81: nas 'bras dkar po las byung ba'i chan sogs kha zas /
NK005(ca)005:82: gzhan yang nag po'i rigs ma 'dres pa'i 'bru sna /
NK005(ca)005:83: tsan dan dkar dmar gur gum sogs dug rigs ma 'dres pa'i sman sna /
NK005(ca)005:84: tsam+pa ka sogs me tog tshogs rang bzhin nam bcos
NK005(ca)005:85: bus kha dog dkar po dang ser por byas pa
NK005(ca)005:86: zhi ba rgyas pa gnyis ga'i rdzas su rung ba
NK005(ca)005:87: rnams tshogs pa 'jig rten pa dang ye shes pa
NK005(ca)005:88: phyi nang gnyis rim du bkod /
NK005(ca)005:89: khyad par gyi rdzas mar khu la mngar gsum btab pa dang /
NK005(ca)005:91: nyams rtogs bskyed phyir chang rag gi snying khu la bdud rtsi chos sman btab pa /
NK005(ca)005:93: stegs bu cig shos la bdag bskyed kyi mchod gtor
NK005(ca)005:94: spyi 'gre dang bye brag sbyin sreg la 'bras chan
NK005(ca)005:95: dngul phye me tog dkar po rnams bsres pa'i mar
NK005(ca)005:96: dkar gyi gtor zlum ril bu gang mang gis bskor
NK005(ca)005:97: ba dang / 'jig rten par yang rgyu gong 'dra'i
NK005(ca)005:98: gtor ma zlum po gcig dang gzhan yang zhabs bsil
NK005(ca)005:99: la sogs pa'i nyer spyod rnams rang bzhin nam /
NK005(ca)005:106: thugs dam bskul ba'i rdzas yungs kar rin po che
NK005(ca)005:107: dkar po'i snod du blugs pa rnams ma tshang ba
NK005(ca)005:109: gnyis pa dngos gzhi'i rim pa ni /
NK005(ca)005:110: gtso bo rdo rje sems dpa'i nga rgyal la gnas
NK005(ca)005:111: bzhin pas rang nyid chas gos dkar po dang ldan
NK005(ca)005:112: pa stan la rdzogs pa'i skyil mo krung gis 'dug
NK005(ca)005:113: nas byang chub kyi sems mchog sgrub pa'i blo dang
NK005(ca)005:114: ldan pas rdor dril bsangs sbyangs /
NK005(ca)005:115: ma h+aa kro d+h+ai shwa ri sarba dra byam bi sho d+ha ni h+aum phata /
NK005(ca)005:117: stong pa'i ngang las h+aum las byung ba'i rdo rje
NK005(ca)005:118: thabs kyi rang bzhin ye shes lnga'i ngo bo dang
NK005(ca)005:119: / +aahls byung ba'i dril bu shes rab kyi rang bzhin stong nyid chos kyi sgra dbyangs sgrogs pa /
NK005(ca)005:120: gnyis ka'ang don dam pa'i byang chub sems kyi rang bzhin no //
NK005(ca)005:123: badz+ra g+han+de +aah zhes dril bu 'khrol zhing dkur brten /
NK005(ca)005:124: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa a nu r+aa ga badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa at+ma ko&a h'u /
NK005(ca)005:126: de nas nyer spyod sman raka bcas la dmigs te /
NK005(ca)005:127: ma h+aa kro d+hi shwa ri sogs kyis bsangs /
NK005(ca)005:128: rang gi thugs ka nas ram yam kham 'phros ye
NK005(ca)005:129: shes kyi me rlung chur gyur pas mchod rdzas kyi
NK005(ca)005:130: dngos 'dzin nyes skyon thams cad bsregs gtor bkrus te
NK005(ca)005:131: stong par gyur / stong pa'i ngang las b+h+r+aum dang
NK005(ca)005:132: +aahls byung ba'i snod bzang por +aahmh'u las las byung
NK005(ca)005:133: ba'i mchod pa'i rdzas rnams 'dod yon gyi khyad par
NK005(ca)005:134: mtha' yas pa rang bzhin bde stong gi ye shes
NK005(ca)005:135: stong par gyur / / rnam pa mchod rdzas kyi sprin phung /
NK005(ca)005:136: byed las dbang po drug zag med kyi bde bas
NK005(ca)005:137: tshim par nus pas nam mkha' gang ba rnams su
NK005(ca)005:140: badz+ra a ha ra h+r+aihn mahsarba ta th+aa ga te
NK005(ca)005:141: b+h+yo a lang k+aa ra pa na pee h+aum s+w+aa
NK005(ca)005:142: h+aa / b+ho b+h+y+aam ga rat+na me g+ha s+pha ra h+aum /
NK005(ca)005:143: +aahh+aum sarba pany+tsa a mri ta h+aum h+r+ai tha /
NK005(ca)005:144: ma h+aa rak+ta dz+wa la man+dala h+aum h+r+ai tha /
NK005(ca)005:145: zhes pas sman raka gnyis brlab /
NK005(ca)005:146: bsreg rdzas rnams la bsangs chu 'thor zhing /
NK005(ca)005:149: stong pa'i ngang las ma dang a las nyi zla'i
NK005(ca)005:150: ga'u'i snod du bsreg rdzas rnams so so'i ming yig
NK005(ca)005:151: dang po thig les brgyan pa 'od du zhu ba
NK005(ca)005:152: las byung ba'i bdud rtsi'i dngos po mchog gi dngos
NK005(ca)005:153: grub sgrub pa la thogs pa med pa'i nus pa
NK005(ca)005:158: de nas thab la dmigs te /
NK005(ca)005:159: ma h+aa kro d+h+ai shwa ri sogs kyis bsangs /
NK005(ca)005:161: stong pa'i ngang las mdun du b+h+r+aum yig 'phro 'dus
NK005(ca)005:162: yongs su gyur pa las 'khor lo'i lte ba la
NK005(ca)005:163: gnas pa'i zhi ba'i thab khung dkar zhing zlum pa
NK005(ca)005:164: kha khyer bang rim dang ldan pa 'od zer dkar
NK005(ca)005:166: rang gi thugs ka nas ram yig thab nang du
NK005(ca)005:167: spros pa las ye shes kyi me 'od dkar po
NK005(ca)005:169: ag+na ye dz+wa la dz+wa la h+aum phata /
NK005(ca)005:170: ces rgyun bzhag gam gtsub shing las byung ba'i mes sbar /
NK005(ca)005:171: thab kyi me'i dbus su ma dang dihls byung ba'i
NK005(ca)005:172: nyi ma dang ra skyes kyi gdan la yig dkar
NK005(ca)005:173: po 'phro 'dus yongs su gyur pa las ag+ni de
NK005(ca)005:174: ba ri shi h+aum zhi ba'i me lha dkar po
NK005(ca)005:175: zhi zhing 'dzum pa drang srong gi cha byad can
NK005(ca)005:176: gun+d+he dang bgrang phreng 'dzin pa'i skur gyur /
NK005(ca)005:178: mgrin par +aah thugs kar h+aum gis mtshan pa las
NK005(ca)005:179: 'od zer 'phros pas shar lho nas me lha 'khor
NK005(ca)005:181: ag+ni de ba sa ma ya h+aum dzah zhes se gol bsnol mar gdab /
NK005(ca)005:182: mda' dar dmar pos g.yabs shing /
NK005(ca)005:183: h+aum dad pa dang ni dam tshig gis //
NK005(ca)005:184: tshur gshegs tshur gshegs 'byung po che //
NK005(ca)005:185: me lha drang srong bram ze mchog /
NK005(ca)005:186: 'di nyid du ni gshegs su gsol //
NK005(ca)005:187: ag+ni de ba ri shi dzahdzah zhes lcags kyu'i rgya dang bcas drangs /
NK005(ca)005:188: dzahh+aum bam ho sa bstims nas /
NK005(ca)005:189: ag+ni de ba ri shi ar+g+ham pra t+aits+tsha hoh de bzhin du push+pe sogs kyis mchod nas /
NK005(ca)005:190: ji ltar bstams pa tsam gyis sogs mthar /
NK005(ca)005:191: sarba ta th+aa ga ta a b+hi sogs brjod de /
NK005(ca)005:193: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas rnams kyi thugs ka nas dbang
NK005(ca)005:194: gi lha mo byang chub sems kyis gang ba'i bum
NK005(ca)005:195: pa thogs pa spros te dbang bskur /
NK005(ca)005:196: rat+na a lam k+aa ra s+w+aa h+aa /
NK005(ca)005:198: me lha zhal 'dzum pa dang bcas pa'i cung zad
NK005(ca)005:199: gdags pa'i ljags dang gzar bu gnyis kyi kha la
NK005(ca)005:200: ram yig 'od zer gyi phung por 'bar bas sreg
NK005(ca)005:201: blugs kyi bdud rtsi'i rgyun drangs nas gsol bar bsams
NK005(ca)005:202: la / lag gnyis byang chub mchog gi rgyas dgang blugs bzung nas /
NK005(ca)005:204: zhes pa bdun gyis dgang gzar bkang la /
NK005(ca)005:205: ag+ni de wa ri shi ha bya ka bya di
NK005(ca)005:206: bya bdag cag dpon slob rnams kyi byang chub sgrub
NK005(ca)005:207: pa la bar du gcod pa'i 'gal rkyen bar chad
NK005(ca)005:208: mi mthun pa'i phyogs thams cad sh+aan+tim ku ru s+w+aa
NK005(ca)005:209: h+aa / zhes lan gsum gyis dgang blugs 'bul /
NK005(ca)005:210: sngags de nyid kyis yam shing sogs rdzas gzhan rnams grangs ci rigs pa phul rjes /
NK005(ca)005:211: h+aum tshangs pa 'jig rten mgon gyi sras //
NK005(ca)005:212: me lha'i rgyal po drang srong tshul //
NK005(ca)005:213: 'byung po yongs su skyob pa'i phyir //
NK005(ca)005:214: thugs rje'i dbang gis sku sprul pa //
NK005(ca)005:215: rig sngags grub pa drang srong tshul //
NK005(ca)005:216: nyon mongs bsregs pas shes rab 'od //
NK005(ca)005:217: bskal pa'i me bzhi gzi brjid 'bar //
NK005(ca)005:218: mngon shes rdzu 'phrul zhabs dang ldan //
NK005(ca)005:219: thabs kyi sprul pa theg pa chibs //
NK005(ca)005:220: bgrang phreng 'dzin cing rig sngags gsung //
NK005(ca)005:221: bdud rtsi'i bcud can gun+d+he bsnams //
NK005(ca)005:222: chos kyi bdud rtsi yongs la bsil //
NK005(ca)005:223: nyes pa'i skyon bral tshangs par spyod //
NK005(ca)005:225: zhi ba brnyes kyang thugs rje che //
NK005(ca)005:226: de la bstod de phyag kyang 'tshal //
NK005(ca)005:228: na mo rig pa'i rgyal po khyod kyis las thams
NK005(ca)005:229: cad byed pas sreg rdzas lha'i zhal du 'bul ba
NK005(ca)005:230: dang / me nyid ye shes kyi mer byin gyis
NK005(ca)005:231: brlabs nas bdag cag dpon slob 'khor dang bcas pa'i
NK005(ca)005:232: byang chub bsgrub pa'i lam gyi bar chad thams cad
NK005(ca)005:233: zhi ba'i 'phrin las mdzad du gsol /
NK005(ca)005:235: de nas 'jig rten las 'das pa'i me lha mchod pa ni /
NK005(ca)005:236: me lha'i lto ba yangs shing rgya che ba'i dbus su yig 'phro 'dus yongs su gyur pa las /
NK005(ca)005:237: phyi rin po che'i gzhal yas khang chen po gru
NK005(ca)005:238: bzhi sgo bzhi rta babs bzhis brgyan pa tshad dang
NK005(ca)005:239: mtshan nyid thams cad yongs su rdzogs pa /
NK005(ca)005:240: khor yug dur khrod dang bcas pa'i nang gzhal med
NK005(ca)005:241: khang gru bzhi sgo bzhi sogs mtshan nyid thams cad
NK005(ca)005:243: pho brang dbus ma rdo rje sems dpa'i dkyil 'khor
NK005(ca)005:244: la dbus su zlum po rdo rje'i mu khyud can
NK005(ca)005:245: / shar du rnam snang gi dkyil 'khor zlum po 'khor lo'i mu khyud can /
NK005(ca)005:246: lhor he ru ka'i dkyil 'khor zla gam sgo gcig
NK005(ca)005:247: shar du lta ba thod pa'i rtsig pa dang khro
NK005(ca)005:248: bo'i rdo rje'i mu khyud can /
NK005(ca)005:249: nub tu gar dbang gi dkyil 'khor pad+ma 'dab ma
NK005(ca)005:250: brgyad pa'i dbyibs can ka ba dang mu khyud la
NK005(ca)005:252: byang du rdo rje nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor rin po
NK005(ca)005:253: che zur brgyad pa'i dbyibs can rin po che'i mu
NK005(ca)005:254: khyud can / mtshams bzhir rta mchog rigs bzhi'i dkyil
NK005(ca)005:255: 'khor sna tshogs rdo rje'i mu khyud can phrin las
NK005(ca)005:256: bzhi'i khyad par las shar dang shar lho /
NK005(ca)005:259: byang dang byang shar rnams mtshungs pa ste /
NK005(ca)005:260: thams cad kyang ling tshe dgu dgu dang ldan pa las /
NK005(ca)005:261: lho dang lho nub kyi ling tshe dgu la zla gam nang bstan dgu dang /
NK005(ca)005:262: zhing gi 'phan gdugs sogs 'jigs pa'i rgyan can /
NK005(ca)005:263: lho ma'i dbus su pad+ma dregs byed nyi zla brtsegs
NK005(ca)005:264: pa dang re'u mig brgyad la bam chen ri'i gdan
NK005(ca)005:265: gyis khyad par du byas pa /
NK005(ca)005:266: dkyil 'khor gzhan rnams kyi dbus kyi ling tshe la
NK005(ca)005:267: pad+ma 'dab ma brgyad pa'i gdan re re'i mtshams kyi
NK005(ca)005:268: 'dab ma rnams la rin po che'i bum pa bdud
NK005(ca)005:269: rtsis gang ba thod pas kha brgyan pa re re
NK005(ca)005:270: / phyogs mtshams kyi re'u mig brgyad dang dkyil 'khor
NK005(ca)005:271: thams cad la mtshungs par sgo bzhi dang gra bzhir
NK005(ca)005:273: skabs 'dir sgrub mjug dang 'brel ba sogs yin na
NK005(ca)005:274: gdan bskyed pa'i rjes de ma thag par spyan 'dren
NK005(ca)005:275: bya ba ni / dmigs med mkha' ltar dag pa khyab pa'i sku //
NK005(ca)005:276: spyan 'dren gshegs su gsol bar mi dmigs kyang //
NK005(ca)005:277: thugs rje'i ngang nyid chos skur dag pa las //
NK005(ca)005:278: ye shes sgyu mar rol cing gshegs su gsol //
NK005(ca)005:279: bsnyengs pa mi mnga' stobs bcu'i shugs ldan cing //
NK005(ca)005:280: ma 'dres sangs rgyas chos rnams rab tu rdzogs //
NK005(ca)005:281: dpa' bo chen po longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku //
NK005(ca)005:282: mkha' 'gro kun dang thabs gcig gshegs su gsol //
NK005(ca)005:283: thugs rje chen po'i sku mnga' gsung nyid rdzogs //
NK005(ca)005:284: mi 'jigs thugs mnga' seng ges bskyod du med //
NK005(ca)005:285: gdug pa'i tshogs kyang zil gyis gnon mdzad pa //
NK005(ca)005:286: bcom ldan 'gro la brtse slad gshegs su gsol //
NK005(ca)005:287: dzahh+aum bam hoh e h+ye hi b+ha ga wan ma
NK005(ca)005:288: h+aa ka ru ni ka dri sh+ya hoh sa ma
NK005(ca)005:289: ya s+t+wam / zhes man+dala me tog gi tshom bu
NK005(ca)005:290: can sogs kyi brdas spyan drangs pa slob dpon la
NK005(ca)005:291: g.yas su bskor te slob dpon gyis me tog thab
NK005(ca)005:292: nang du dor ba dang lhan cig tu /
NK005(ca)005:293: lha tshogs rnams rang rang gi gdan la bzhugs par bsams te /
NK005(ca)005:294: ma h+aa su kha badz+ra sa t+wa +aahdzahh+aum bam ho su ra ta s+t+wam /
NK005(ca)005:295: zhes thun mong min pa rdor sems kyi snying po yi ge bco brgyad pa'o //
NK005(ca)005:299: he ru ka badz+ra sa ma ya h+r+aihsarba dush+tana sa
NK005(ca)005:300: ma ya mu dra pra b+hany+dza ka h'u phatah he
NK005(ca)005:301: ru ka'i'o // swa b+h+aa wa shud+d+ha sarba d+harma narti shwa ra h+r+aihdzah gar dbang gi'o //
NK005(ca)005:302: sid+d+hin+tuhsa ma ya sid+d+h+ya ma h+aa badz+ra rat+na ba ba ta ta t+r+aam /
NK005(ca)005:304: sum b+ha ni sum b+ha h'u /
NK005(ca)005:306: zhes sngags tsam mam mngon rtogs kyis gsal gdab pa ni /
NK005(ca)005:308: dkyil 'khor dbus ma'i lte bar dpal rdo rje sems dpa' bde ba chen po'i lha tshogs /
NK005(ca)005:309: dkyil 'khor shar ma'i dbus su rgyal ba rtag pa rnam par snang mdzad kyi lha tshogs /
NK005(ca)005:310: dkyil 'khor lho ma'i dbus su dpal chen he ru ka'i lha tshogs /
NK005(ca)005:311: dkyil 'khor nub ma'i dbus su pad+ma gar gyi dbang phyug gi lha tshogs /
NK005(ca)005:312: dkyil 'khor byang ma'i dbus su rdo rje nyi ma'i lha tshogs /
NK005(ca)005:313: mtshams bzhi'i dkyil 'khor gyi dbus su rta mchog rol
NK005(ca)005:314: pa'i sangs rgyas kyi lha tshogs thams cad sku dngas
NK005(ca)005:315: pa'i mtsho la gza' skar shar ba bzhin bzhugs pa'i
NK005(ca)005:316: sku las 'od zer dkar po'i tshogs mkha' khyab tu
NK005(ca)005:317: spro ba'i bdag nyid can du snang ba'o //
NK005(ca)005:318: sreg rkyang gi skabs su gzhal yas khang gdan bcas
NK005(ca)005:319: gong bzhin gyi rjes las byang nas de man gyi
NK005(ca)005:320: mngon rtogs spyan 'dren bzhugs gsol grub nas /
NK005(ca)005:322: stong gsum stong gi 'jig rten na //
NK005(ca)005:323: phyogs bzhi'i dkyil 'khor dbus rnams kyi //
NK005(ca)005:324: skye 'gro rdul snyed gnas pa kun //
NK005(ca)005:325: bde gshegs lha yi dkyil 'khor dbyings //
NK005(ca)005:326: phyogs dus kun nas tshogs pa'i lha //
NK005(ca)005:327: gnyis su med par phyag 'tshal lo //
NK005(ca)005:329: a ti b+h+au hoh ban+d+ha ka ro mi gu ru pa ti a la la hoh zhes phyag bya'o //
NK005(ca)005:330: mchod pa'i dang po sprul pa ni /
NK005(ca)005:332: stong gsum rdul snyed ma lus pa'i //
NK005(ca)005:333: gzugs sgra dri ro reg bya chos //
NK005(ca)005:334: lha mo'i tshogs rnams ma lus spro //
NK005(ca)005:335: me tog bdug pa mar me ma //
NK005(ca)005:336: dri mchog kun gyis mchod par bya //
NK005(ca)005:337: pa na pe pe nu su ra ta ti pu
NK005(ca)005:338: ba ra mu sarba ta th+aa ga ta sa ma
NK005(ca)005:341: gnyis pa 'bul ba nih badz+ra push+pe /
NK005(ca)005:345: pra t+aits+tsha hoh sh+r+ai b+ha ga w+aan /
NK005(ca)005:353: badz+ra sa ma ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK005(ca)005:356: dkyil 'khor gyi lha rnams kyi ljags rdo rje 'od
NK005(ca)005:357: kyi sbu gu can gyis sreg blugs kyi bdud rtsi'i
NK005(ca)005:358: rgyun drangs nas gsol bar gyur par bsams la /
NK005(ca)005:359: ma h+aa su kha badz+ra sa t+wa +aahdza h'u bam hohsu ra ta stam /
NK005(ca)005:360: lan bdun gyis dgang gzar bkang la /
NK005(ca)005:361: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa mu dra p+auts+tsha ho /
NK005(ca)005:362: bdag dang 'gro ba sems can thams cad kyi //
NK005(ca)005:363: sgrib gnyis byang zhing tshogs gnyis myur du rdzogs //
NK005(ca)005:364: sa bcu lam lnga'i yon tan mthar phyin nas //
NK005(ca)005:365: phyag rgya chen po mchog gi dngos grub stsol //
NK005(ca)005:366: zhes 'dod gsol sbyar la lan gsum 'bul /
NK005(ca)005:367: de nas yam shing mar khu sogs rdzas gzhan rnams 'khor los bsgyur ba drug gi spyi sngags /
NK005(ca)005:368: badz+ra sa t+wa ma h+aa sa ma ya +aahmh'u s+w+aa h+aa /
NK005(ca)005:369: zhes pas ji ltar rigs pa 'bul zhing /
NK005(ca)005:370: bcu tshan re'i mthar 'dod gsol snga ma bzhin sbyar /
NK005(ca)005:372: lha tshogs rnams kyi sku las zla ba chu shel
NK005(ca)005:373: lta bu'i 'od zer byung ba rang la phog pas
NK005(ca)005:374: nyon mongs pa dang shes bya'i sgrib pa sbyangs /
NK005(ca)005:375: sa dang lam gyi yon tan mthar phyin nas phyag
NK005(ca)005:376: rgya chen po mchog gi dngos grub thob par bsam
NK005(ca)005:377: mo // de nas de la kha dog legs bsgyur ba'i //
NK005(ca)005:378: na bza' shin tu dri zhim dam pa 'bul //
NK005(ca)005:381: badz+ra tam+bu la ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK005(ca)005:385: sogs kyis rnam pa bdun phul /
NK005(ca)005:386: sh+r+ai badz+ra sa pa ri w+aa ra ma h+aa b+ha ling ta kh+aa hi /
NK005(ca)005:387: ma h+aa sarba pany+tsa a mri ta kh+aa hi /
NK005(ca)005:390: sangs rgyas thams cad mnyam sbyor ba //
NK005(ca)005:391: mkha' 'gro sgyu ma bde ba'i mchog /
NK005(ca)005:393: che ba'i lha la phyag 'tshal mchod //
NK005(ca)005:394: 'khor ba'i nyes pas ma gos shing //
NK005(ca)005:395: 'gro la rjes su chags pa'i sku //
NK005(ca)005:396: zla ba ltar dkar rtsa dmar 'gying //
NK005(ca)005:397: rdor sems bde ba che la 'dud //
NK005(ca)005:398: stong pa ma yin mi stong min //
NK005(ca)005:399: dbu ma'i lam la rab 'jog pa //
NK005(ca)005:400: gti mug rgya mtsho zhi bar mdzad //
NK005(ca)005:401: rgyal ba rtag pa la phyag 'tshal //
NK005(ca)005:402: shin tu gdul dka' drag po la //
NK005(ca)005:403: zhi bas phan par mi 'gyur bas //
NK005(ca)005:404: de bzhin gshegs kun khro bor gyur //
NK005(ca)005:406: chags chen rdo rje chos kyi sku //
NK005(ca)005:407: lta ba ngan rnams sbyong ba'i phyir //
NK005(ca)005:408: sgyu ma sna tshogs tshul ston pa //
NK005(ca)005:410: yid bzhin nor bu sbyin pa po //
NK005(ca)005:411: ser sna zil gnon 'gro ba sgrol //
NK005(ca)005:412: bsam pa thams cad rdzogs mdzad pa //
NK005(ca)005:413: rdo rje nyi ma la phyag 'tshal //
NK005(ca)005:414: rdo rje las ni brtson 'grus che //
NK005(ca)005:415: khro dang nga rgyal le lo 'joms //
NK005(ca)005:416: pha rol gnon pa shin tu stobs //
NK005(ca)005:417: rta mchog dpal la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK005(ca)005:418: ces bstod cing las gzhung ltar tshogs kyi 'khor los dgyes pa bskyed nas /
NK005(ca)005:421: byin rlabs kun gyi rtsa ba bla ma ni //
NK005(ca)005:422: dngos grub stsol phyir 'khor lo drug gi lha //
NK005(ca)005:423: rnam thar sgo gsum thugs kyi dkyil 'khor nas //
NK005(ca)005:424: rang bzhin yongs grub byang chub sems kyi dngos //
NK005(ca)005:425: phyag rgya chen po mchog gi dngos grub stsol //
NK005(ca)005:426: sa bcu lam lnga dbang bcu phyi nang gnyis //
NK005(ca)005:427: rig 'dzin bzhi dang sku lnga ye shes lnga //
NK005(ca)005:428: grub pa brgyad dang phrin las rnam pa bzhi //
NK005(ca)005:429: 'khor ba'i rang bzhin glo bur sgrib pa gnyis //
NK005(ca)005:430: kun gzhi'i khams la bag la nyal gyi tshul //
NK005(ca)005:431: shin tu rnam dag rnam kun mchog ldan gyi //
NK005(ca)005:432: dngos grub dam pa deng 'dir stsal du gsol //
NK005(ca)005:436: nir+m+aa k+aa ya tsit+ta sid+d+hi pha la h+aum /
NK005(ca)005:438: slar yang gtang rag gi mchod pa /
NK005(ca)005:441: badz+ra d+hu pe badz+ra gan+d+he badz+ra nee wit+ya badz+ra sa ma ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK005(ca)005:445: 'di ni sangs rgyas thams cad kyi //
NK005(ca)005:446: yang dag yon tan rgya chen te //
NK005(ca)005:447: lan gcig tsam zhig brjod pas kyang //
NK005(ca)005:450: yi ge brgya pas nongs pa bzod par gsol zhing /
NK005(ca)005:451: sngar ltar me tog gis spyan drangs te /
NK005(ca)005:452: dkyil 'khor pa'i lha tshogs sgrub pa'i dkyil 'khor la gshegs /
NK005(ca)005:453: gzhal yas khang dang bcas pa rang la thim par gyur /
NK005(ca)005:454: sgrub mchod rab gnas sogs dang ma 'brel ba'i sreg rkyang gi tshe gong gi tshab tu //
NK005(ca)005:455: khyed kyis sems can sogs kyis gshegs gsol dang dam tshig pa rang la bstim /
NK005(ca)005:457: ag+ni ye dz+wa la dz+wa la h+aum phata /
NK005(ca)005:458: ces blugs gzar gyi me gsos nas /
NK005(ca)005:459: ag+ne de bi ra shi ha bya ka bya de
NK005(ca)005:460: bya bdag cag dpon slob rnams kyi byang chub sgrub
NK005(ca)005:461: pa la bar du gcod pa'i 'gal rkyen mi mthun
NK005(ca)005:462: pa'i phyogs thams cad sh+aan+tim ku ru s+w+aa h+aa /
NK005(ca)005:464: badz+ra tam bu las so rtsi phul /
NK005(ca)005:466: ag+ne de wa ri shi ar+g+ham sogs kyis nyer spyod dang /
NK005(ca)005:467: ag+ne de wa ri shi ma h+aa ba lim ta kh+aa hi /
NK005(ca)005:468: ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta kh+aa hi /
NK005(ca)005:472: ma brnyed yongs sogs kyis bzod par gsol /
NK005(ca)005:473: badz+ra muhs ye shes pa rang gnas su gshags /
NK005(ca)005:474: dam tshig pa 'bar ba'i rnam par gyur par bsam /
NK005(ca)005:475: gsum pa rjes kyi rim pas mjug bsdu ba ni /
NK005(ca)005:477: shis brjod spyi khyab ltar bya zhing /
NK005(ca)005:478: sreg rkyang gi tshe bdag bskyed kyi mjug chog kyang bya'o //
NK005(ca)005:479: sbyin sreg gi me rang zhir 'jog pa'am /
NK005(ca)005:480: long khyab kyis ma khams na 'o ma dang dri bzang po'i chus gzhil nas /
NK005(ca)005:481: thal ba 'bab chu'am ri mthon po'i rtser bskyal la las kyi rjes mi mngon par bya'o //
NK005(ca)005:482: de ltar mchog gi sbyin sreg mnyam sbyor la brten
NK005(ca)005:483: pa 'di ni sgrub mchod chen mo'i skabs su nye
NK005(ca)005:484: bar mkho bar mthong nas kun mkhyen 'jigs med gling
NK005(ca)005:485: pa'i gsung las tshig phrad cung zad bsgyur nas rig
NK005(ca)005:486: 'dzin tshe dbang mchog grub kyis bklag chog mar bkral
